<title>ạllh ạlly ʿm yjmʿkn</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- ạllh ạlly ʿm yjmʿkn hwy ạlly rḥ ymsẖy mʿkn ʿ drwb ạlḥyạẗ
 mạtkẖạfwạ mn bkrạ ạljạyy wlạ mn sẖy mṣybẗ mkẖbạyẗ
 btḥmlhạ ạlsạʿạt whmwm ạlʿạlm klạ hwy wḥdh byḥlạaⁿ
 ʿnkn msẖ rḥ ytkẖly̱ rḥ ystrkn bạlḍyqạt
 1- yạ ạ̹kẖty klmẗ ạllh btwṣyky ạ̹nw tkwny wfyẗ bkl ạlạ̉ḥwạl
 kẖly yswʿ mṣwr dạymạaⁿ fyky ạllh mwṣy tạ ạlmrạ̉ẗ tṭyʿ ạlrjạl
 kwny llʿylẗ klạ sẖhạdẗ ʿn nʿmẗ ạllh
 kẖlly bytk ybqy̱ knysẗ ttʿysẖwạ sẖbh ạlạ̉bṭạl ạkylạ wbryskylạ
 2- yạkẖyy ạljạzẗ sẖrkẗ byn tlạtẗ ạnt wmrtk mạ tnswạ ạllh ạlạ̉sạs
 hwy wḥdh ạlly ḍạmn bkrh ạlậty wḥdh ạlbykẖly bytk mrfwʿ ạlrạs
 mrtk ḥbạ wdạryhạ bbbw ʿynk kẖbyhạ
 tsẖbh byswʿ tʿlm nfsh ʿn ạlknysẗ qdm ḥty̱ bdmh yfdyhạ</lyrics>
</song>